00:38:16.170 --> 00:38:21.240
dehumidification and
adaptive ventilation.

00:38:21.240 --> 00:38:25.680
Heating right, it's a kind
of counterintuitive thing,

00:38:25.680 --> 00:38:27.890
in the summertime and Biloxi
would we actually turn

00:38:27.890 --> 00:38:34.330
up the heat, but warm air holds
more moisture than cold air

00:38:34.330 --> 00:38:36.870
so there's an option
