and rapidly dries

00:38:50.860 --> 00:38:54.660
out everything, everything.

00:38:55.740 --> 00:39:01.290
Adaptive ventilation promotes
drying, so air passing

00:39:01.290 --> 00:39:03.930
over a wet surface
retains water.

00:39:03.930 --> 00:39:07.870
According to a 2004
study by Tim Padfield,

00:39:07.870 --> 00:39:11.110
moving air becomes completely
saturated when it passes

00:39:11.110 --> 00:39:15.230
over wet material
regardless of the air's speed.

00:39:15.230 --> 00:39:19.190
So, airflow changes surface
tension causing evaporation

00:39:19.190 --> 00:39:22.090
that can prevent
fungal growth in caves,

00:39:22.090 --> 00:39:25.310
elementary schools
and in my lungs.

00:39:25.310 --> 00:39:29.020
Tyvek envelopes, sealed
glass exhibit cases,

00:39:29.020 --> 00:39:30.340
