success repairing that pipe

00:46:13.400 --> 00:46:18.280
out on the street and so maybe
that source of water is gone,

00:46:18.280 --> 00:46:22.260
but I think the water inside
the building is still a

00:46:22.260 --> 00:46:24.200
major problem.

00:46:24.200 --> 00:46:27.270
